                    items: [
                        { id: 'e1-1', name: 'Analytics aggregation engine', status: 'planned', category: 'infrastructure', priority: 'critical', notes: 'Track aggregated skills trends, intent signals, match patterns across all users. Time-series storage for supply/demand indices. Foundation for all enterprise intelligence.' },
                        { id: 'e1-2', name: 'User consent framework', status: 'planned', category: 'infrastructure', priority: 'critical', notes: 'Explicit opt-in for anonymized data contribution and discoverable talent pool. Granular controls: what\'s visible, who can see it, revocable at any time. GDPR compliant. Not a checkbox — informed, contextual consent.' },
                        { id: 'e1-3', name: 'Skills ontology cross-mapping', status: 'in-progress', category: 'infrastructure', priority: 'high', notes: 'v4.45.24: Skills library v4 now includes ESCO (13,939), Lightcast (28,955), O*NET (139), and Trades (30) in unified index. v4.45.25: Lightcast skills recategorized into ESCO-style categories via 80+ regex rules. External synonym layer bridges terminology differences (670+ mappings). Remaining: formal SFIA mapping, bidirectional taxonomy API for enterprise customers, and categorization refinement for skills still in General Professional.' },
                        { id: 'e1-4', name: 'Recruiter-facing report landing page', status: 'planned', category: 'feature', priority: 'high', notes: 'Polish the shared scouting report viewer for recruiter UX. Add CTA for recruiter registration. Track engagement (view duration, sections read, shortlist clicks). Currently functional but not optimized for conversion.' },
                        { id: 'e1-5', name: 'Anonymization engine', status: 'planned', category: 'infrastructure', priority: 'critical', notes: 'Minimum cohort size of 50 for any aggregate query. k-anonymity for any exposed data slice. PII stripping pipeline. Differential privacy for small-n edge cases. Enterprise customers never see individual data without mutual consent.' },
                        { id: 'e1-6', name: 'Terms of Service & Privacy Policy update', status: 'planned', category: 'legal', priority: 'critical', notes: 'Update ToS for enterprise data licensing. Privacy policy must clearly explain anonymized aggregation, consent model, and user rights. Legal review required before any enterprise feature launches.' }
                    ]
